n="0778a07" ed="T"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0778a07"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012299"><placeName>杭州</placeName><placeName>大慈山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010538">寰中</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0778a08"/><persName key="A010538">釋寰中</persName>，姓<name>盧</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005199"><placeName>河東</placeName><placeName>蒲坂</placeName></placeName>人也。稟靈<anchor xml:id="beg0778001"/>特<anchor xml:id="end0778001"/>異，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a09"/>挺質殊倫，身支𦟛亭，頂骨圓峻，其聲若鐘響，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a10"/>其色猶脂凝。學通終古，辭實豐贍。<date key="j20147152015080" from-iso="+0804-01-01" to-iso="+0804-12-31">年二十<lb
ed="T" n="0778a11"/>五</date>，隨計中甲科<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1579"/>，然未塞其懷，復思再捷。無<lb
ed="T" n="0778a12"/>何，遭母之憂，遂廬于墓所。及服闋，徑往<placeName key="PL000000003780"><placeName>北<lb
ed="T" n="0778a13"/>京</placeName><placeName>童子寺</placeName></placeName>出家。二稔未周，諸經皆覽。明年，往<lb
ed="T" n="0778a14"/><placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩嶽</placeName>登戒，<anchor xml:id="beg0778002"/>肄習<anchor xml:id="end0778002"/>律部。於茲博通，忽慕上乘，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a15"/>決往<placeName key="PL000000019628">百丈山</placeName>，深得玄旨。後隱<placeName key="PL000000028944"><placeName>南嶽</placeName><placeName>常樂寺</placeName></placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a16"/>結茅于山椒。諫議大夫<persName key="A010539"><anchor xml:id="beg0778sgsz3"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>崖</sic><corr>崔</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0778sgsz3"/><roleName>公</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n1584"/>深重其操，因別<lb
ed="T" n="0778a17"/>立方丈。虞淵<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1580"/>景晞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1581"/>，一飯永日。然其乏水，羸<lb
ed="T" n="0778a18"/>瓶遠求。俄爾深宵，有虎嘷嘯廬側，詰旦視<lb
ed="T" n="0778a19"/>之，果濫泉坼地而湧，足其汲用<ptr target="#n927"/>。後之<placeName key="PL000000011519">杭</placeName>，<placeName key="PL000000008367">浙<lb
ed="T" n="0778a20"/>江</placeName>之北有山號<placeName key="PL000000012299">大慈</placeName><ptr target="#n1585"/>。居未久，檀信爰臻。旋<lb
ed="T" n="0778a21"/>成巨院，四方僧侶參禮如雲。<date from-iso="+0840-02-14" key="j20279082030170" to-iso="+0846-04-25">屬</date><persName key="A006570">武宗</persName>廢教，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a22"/><persName key="A010538">中</persName>衣短褐，或請居<persName key="A022977">戴<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>別墅焉。<date from-iso="+0852-01-29" key="j20322752032658" to-iso="+0853-02-15"><name>大中</name>壬申<lb
ed="T" n="0778a23"/>歲</date>，太守<persName key="A022978">劉<roleName>公</roleName></persName>首命剃染<ptr type="glossary" target="#g30"/>，重盛禪林。<date key="j20359812035981" when-iso="+0862-03-23">壬午歲二<lb
ed="T" n="0778a24"/>月十五日</date>囑累，聲畢而終。時漸溽暑，驗其身<lb
ed="T" n="0778a25"/>一無變異，而頂門燠潤。<date from-iso="+0862-10-31" key="j20362032036290" to-iso="+0863-01-26">冬</date>，窆于塔所，享年<lb
ed="T" n="0778a26"/>八十三，法臘五十四<ptr target="#n1586"/>。有說：<placeName key="PL000000028944">常樂寺</placeName>山<placeName key="PL000000028925">虎跑泉</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0778a27"/>當<persName key="A010538">中<roleName>公</roleName></persName>滅日，忽焉乾涸。異哉！止資<persName key="A010538">中</persName>之受<lb
ed="T" n="0778a28"/>用耳。至<date from-iso="+0877-01-22" key="j20414002041783" to-iso="+0878-02-09"><name>乾符</name>丁酉歲</date>，勅謚「大師」，號<persName key="A010538">性空</persName>，塔<lb
ed="T" n="0778a29"/>名<placeName key="PL000000057045">定慧</placeName>也。<placeName key="PL000000014935">縉雲</placeName>太守<persName key="A000850">段成式</persName>為真讚焉。</p>
